{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十五回\"吃人的蝎子\"讲述蓝蝎子为夺回伊哭之死的账目，来到孙驼子的酒馆要带走李寻欢。蓝蝎子带来\"活霸王\"楚相羽作为帮手，却在众人面前以蝎尾暗器一招将其杀死，展示惊人毒辣的武功。孙驼子与蓝蝎子展开激战，蓝蝎子以媚态惑人、蝎尾毒刃周旋。孙驼子以大鹰爪力和驼峰撞技应对，两人交手难分高下。关键时刻蓝蝎子亮出蝎子尾毒刃，孙驼子欲以大鹰爪力夺刃。危急时刻，看似烂醉的李寻欢突然出手，折断蓝蝎子手腕，夺下毒刃，小李飞刀再现江湖。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不错，你的确已不小了，上次我看到你的时候，你还只有五六岁，但现在你已经是大人了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔已有十三四年没有回过家了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不错，十四年，还差几天就是十四年。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔为什么不回家去瞧瞧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我既已答应在这里替人家守护十五年，就得在这里十五年，连一天都不能少，我们这种人说出来的话，就得像钉子钉在墙上一样牢靠，这道理你明不明白？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "这些年来，家里的人都还好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "都很好，大嫂和三嫂今年都添了宝宝，最妙的是，四婶居然也生了对双胞胎，所以今年四叔和大哥、三哥，都一定会赶回去过年……今年过年一定会比往年更热闹多了……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "大家都在盼望着二叔能快些回去，不知道……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你回去告诉他们，等明年过年的时候，我也可以回去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "那好极了，我还记得二叔做的烟花最好……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "明年我一定替你做，但现在……现在你还是快走吧，免得你爷爷等得着急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但这么大一个人，你怎么能带得走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我就当他是条醉猫，往身上一挂就行了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可以走，但这条醉猫却得留下来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "蓝蝎子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你真是好眼力，有眼光的男人，我总是喜欢的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "但我的眼光也不错，我也知道你们是谁了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你既然知道，居然还敢来？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我本也不愿得罪你们，但这醉猫我却非带走不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你也许不知道，我要找个能令我满意的男人有多么困难，好容易才找到一个，却被这醉猫杀死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "伊哭可不是他杀死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "无论是不是他杀死的，这笔账我却已算到他身上。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "无论你怎么样算账，都休想带走他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我也知道你们不会这么容易让我带他走的，我又不太愿意跟你们动手，这怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们可认得他是谁么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "我认得他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你真的认得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "他姓楚，叫楚相羽，外号叫'活霸王'，是京城'洪运镖局'的总镖头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "连这位小妹妹都认得你，看来你的名头可真不小。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "江湖中有名气的人，大大小小我倒差不多全认识，但我却不知道这位楚总镖头怎么会和你走在一起的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是在路上吊上我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "我就是看上他这把胡子，才乖乖地跟着他走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "是他吊上了你，还是你吊上了他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是他吊上我……你们只知道楚大镖头的名气响、武功高，却不知道他吊女人的本事更是高人一筹。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你带这人来干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "一个人能当得了总镖头，武功自然是不错的了，是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位楚大镖头掌中一柄九环刀，的确得过真传，'九九八十一手万胜连环刀'使出来，七八十个人也休想近得了他的身。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若说我一招就能要他的命，你们信不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "我也没说什么，只不过说想要你的命而已。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你在说笑话。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "常言道，一夜夫妻百夜恩，你自然以为我不会杀你的，是吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "我知道你在开玩笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "但你可知道世上有种毒虫叫'蝎子'么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "我怎么会不知道，蝎子在我们北方最多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "那么，你知不知道母蝎子却有种奇怪的毛病。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "什么毛病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "我告诉你，母蝎子和公蝎子交配之后，一定要将公蝎子吃掉才过瘾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "但你却不是蝎子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "谁说我不是蝎子？我明明是蓝蝎子呀，你不知道？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "我劝你，下次你若想在路上吊女人，最好先弄清楚她的底细，只可惜……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "只可惜你已永远没有下次了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "楚相羽",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "站住，你再往前走一步，我就宰了你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_chu_xiang_yu",
      "text": "好，你宰了我吧，我倒真想死在你手里。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只用了一招，你们现在总该相信了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的武功还算不错吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伊哭的青魔手虽然在兵器谱中名列第九，但百晓生若是将我也算上，他至少要退到第十，两位说对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "凭我这样的武功，总可以将这醉猫带走了吧？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "不可以！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我究竟要怎么样才能将他带走呢？难道要我陪你上床？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你不但眼光高，武功也高，只要你说一声，什么地方我都跟你去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你去死吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我要死，也得死在床上！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "还等什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你就算一定要逼我出手，先看看我用的兵刃也不迟呀。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "原来你没有醉。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 402,
